    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <% [
        {name: "Bradley Huet", role: "Parent", initial: "B", rating: 5, text: "Nicole has been working with my son who was failing at afrikaans, she came in and within one term has turned his grade to a pass. I highly recommend Smarty Pants as an affordable and effective solution to picking up your child's grade. An absolute pleasure to work with them and looking forward to great results this year."},
        {name: "Selaelo Chiloane", role: "Parent", initial: "S", rating: 5, text: "Great teachers. They are very patient with the kids and they went all out to assist my daughter to achieve the best results. 10/10â€¦. I would definitely recommend for kids struggling with Afrikaans."},
        {name: "Charleen Tiriwokunze Kulube", role: "Parent", initial: "C", rating: 5, text: "Nicole has been awesome l highly recommend her. My daughter has been doing afrikaans with her and she has improved and is more confident in the subject. l love how she is patient and takes time to understand her students. Thank you Nicole for 2024 looking forward to another year."},
        {name: "Resin Realm", role: "Parent", initial: "R", rating: 5, text: "I highly recommend Nicole for Afrikaans lessons! Nicole is an exceptional teacher who provides personalised attention & patience. With Nicole I've seen improvement in my sons Afrikaans skills, from grammar to conversation. Nicole makes learning enjoyable and effective. If you're seeking a dedicated and knowledgeable Afrikaans tutor, look no further! Nicole is outstanding. Thank you."},
        {name: "Sarah Johnson", role: "Parent", initial: "S", rating: 5, text: "My daughter's confidence in Mathematics has grown tremendously since starting with Smarty Pants. The personalized approach really makes a difference. Her grades have improved from a C to an A in just two terms!"},
